authentication.description:
Enter the Local Key for your device.

**Device:** {device_name}
**Device ID:** {device_id}
**IP Address:** {ip_address}

**How to get the Local Key:**
The Local Key is retrieved from the Tuya IoT Platform. Follow our setup guide to configure API access.

[Setup Guide](https://github.com/moag1000/HA-kkt-kolbe-integration#-tuya-api-setup---vollstaendige-anleitung) | [Tuya IoT Platform](https://iot.tuya.com)

zeroconf_confirm.description:
A KKT Kolbe device was automatically discovered on your network.

**Device:** {device_name}
**Device ID:** {device_id}
**IP Address:** {ip_address}
**Type:** {product_name}

Click Submit to add this device.

zeroconf_authenticate.description:
A device was discovered but requires authentication.

**Device:** {device_name}
**Device ID:** {device_id}
**IP Address:** {ip_address}

**How to get the Local Key:**
The Local Key is a 16-character encryption key from the Tuya IoT Platform.

[Setup Guide](https://github.com/moag1000/HA-kkt-kolbe-integration#-tuya-api-setup---vollstaendige-anleitung) | [Tuya IoT Platform](https://iot.tuya.com)

**Alternative:** Configure API credentials to automatically retrieve the Local Key.

