update_device.description:
The device **{entry_title}** appears to have a new Device ID.

This happens when a device is removed and re-added to Tuya/SmartLife.

**Old Device ID:** {old_device_id}
**Detected New ID:** {new_device_id}
**Old IP:** {old_ip}
**Detected New IP:** {new_ip}

Enable 'Fetch from Cloud' to automatically retrieve the new local key, or enter it manually.
